1. ip
Modern replacement for ifconfig and route.
ip addr show        # Show IP addresses
ip link show        # Show network interfaces
ip route show       # Show routing table
ip link set eth0 up # Bring interface up

2. ping
Checks connectivity between systems.
ping google.com
ping 8.8.8.8

3. ss
Displays socket and port information (replacement for netstat).
ss -tuln            # Show listening ports
ss -tn              # Show active TCP connections

4. netstat (legacy but still asked)
Shows network connections and ports.
netstat -tuln
netstat -rn

5. curl
Transfers data from or to a server (API & web testing).
curl google.com
curl -I google.com  # Show HTTP headers



